{"tid":2040411,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【笑話】美帝智捉共諜","createTime":"2020-05-28T14:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T10:23:36.000Z","uid":354490,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a6663305a1c176544d73dcd398a2f1e98314e56f","tid":2040411,"uid":354490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"有一日<br />\nCIA捉咗一大班國內嘅黃種人<br />\n希望搵出當中嘅共諜<br />\n但奈何無足夠資料<br />\n確定唔到邊一位先係真正共諜<br />\n<br />\n當一班CIA苦無對策嘅時候<br />\n其中一個就講啦<br />\n：「其實你哋唔使咁苦惱，好簡單，畀啲被鋪佢哋，叫佢哋喺度過一晚，第二朝你哋過嚟檢查一下，咁就一清二楚。」<br />\n<br />\n如是者<br />\nCIA真係跟住咁做<br />\n第二日就好順利搵晒所有共諜<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"ec0275a5b29f4aa45c7306a3a904e6842496a0d6","tid":2040411,"uid":122601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:05:49.000Z","msg":"俾d屎佢地，第2日乾乾淨淨就代表係共碟"},{"pid":"76f23eba829f16990e3569ce4c120e6aab01bbf9","tid":2040411,"uid":165336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"因為摺被？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cc2f5798c9172c8ade8d612f5bfd2958869e92","tid":2040411,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"笑話....<br />\n當過兵有record點做間諜呀<br />\n個腦坐住咗？"},{"pid":"4b66196d2eee1f9d96d61a400e81e9425fa02b0f","tid":2040411,"uid":55554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8cc2f5798c9172c8ade8d612f5bfd2958869e92","tid":2040411,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"笑話....<br />\n當過兵有record點做間諜呀<br />\n個腦坐住咗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"呢個好笑"}]}